'''布里斯托尔千禧广场'''（Millennium Square）位于[[英格兰|英格兰]][[布里斯托尔|布里斯托尔]]市中心<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bris.ac.uk/citybristol/gallery/places.html |title=The city of Bristol: Places: Millennium Square |publisher=Bristol University |accessdate=13 August 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120111043313/http://www.bris.ac.uk/citybristol/gallery/places.html |archive-date=2012-01-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，已成为一个受欢迎的公共区域。

千禧广场拥有[[BBC|BBC]]大屏幕<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/bigscreens/locations/bristol/ |title=Big Screens - Bristol |publisher=BBC |date= |accessdate=2012-01-30 |archive-date=2013-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130630024917/http://www.bbc.co.uk/bigscreens/locations/bristol/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 和大型人工水景。布里斯托尔出生的演员[[加里·格兰特|加里·格兰特]]的铜像，由雕塑家格雷厄姆·伊贝森创作，2001年由格兰特的遗孀揭幕。<ref>{{cite news|title=Bristol celebrates Hollywood 'son'|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/1698067.stm|newspaper=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=8 December 2001|accessdate=2021-01-01|archive-date=2003-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031106170209/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/1698067.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 另外三尊青铜雕塑包括[[威廉·佩恩|威廉·佩恩]]、[[威廉·廷代尔|威廉·廷代尔]]和托马斯·查特顿，都是劳伦斯·霍洛夫塞纳的作品。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.at-bristol.org.uk/williampenn.html |title=Penn, Tyndale and Chatterton by Lawrence Holofcener |access-date=2021-01-01 |archive-date=2010-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101203233456/https://www.at-bristol.org.uk/williampenn.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 还有卡西·皮尔金顿的一些彩绘青铜小[[傑克羅素㹴|傑克羅素㹴]]，其中一些仿佛在游泳<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.at-bristol.org.uk/billandbob.html |title=Bill and Bob by Cathie Pilkington |access-date=2021-01-01 |archive-date=2012-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120924005032/http://www.at-bristol.org.uk/billandbob.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

在铺路板中内置了[[日行跡|日行跡]]。

